text.tspan: Jacket Right pieces are shown above.
1. Make mirror copy of Jacket Right pieces for Jacket Left pieces
2. Sew Left & Right Jacket Backs together down Center Back seam
3. Sew Pocket Flap to Jacket Front along Pocket Line
6. Sew Jacket Front & Back together at Shoulder seam
7. Sew Left & Right Under Collars together down Center Back Neck seam
8. Sew Left & Right Upper Collars together down Center Back Neck seam
9. Sew Under Collar to Jacket neck along curved Neck seam, matching seams at Center Back, ending at Lapel Points
10. Sew Upper Collar to Under Collar along Lapel seam, matching seams at Center Back. At Lapel points, continue sewing down Lapel seam to bottom of jacket
11. Sew Jacket Front & Back together at Left & Right Side seams
12. Sew Upper Sleeve to Under Sleeve down front & back seams
